11 garbage container sites have been designated in West Harlem

The New York City Council has installed garbage containers at 11 public schools in West Harlem. Containers have also been set up on the streets highlighted in yellow.

10. Teachers College Community School

11. P.S. 036 Margaret Douglas

Source: District 7 Council Member Shaun Abreu.
